import React from 'react';
import { Routes, Route,Link} from 'react-router-dom'
import Login from './auth/Login'
import Register from './auth/Register'
import ForgotPassword from '../body/auth/ForgotPassword'
import ResetPassword from '../body/auth/ResetPassword'


function Body() {
    return (
        <section>
            <Routes>
                <Route path="/login" element={<Login/>} exact />
                <Route path="/register" element={<Register />} exact />
                <Route path="/forgot_password" element={<ForgotPassword />} exact />
                <Route path="/reset_password" element={<ResetPassword />} exact />
            </Routes>
        </section>
    )
}

export default Body
